metadata.title: FROGG TOGGS Men's Outlander Camp Shoe Footwear
features: 100% waterproof shoe perfect for fishing, hiking, camping and more outdoor activities
description: The Frogg Toggs Outlander Camp Shoe is a 100% waterproof shoe with pull-on tabs. The 5mm neoprene breathable mesh lining and stretch-fit topline keep the wearer comfortable. The shoe also features a self-cleaning patterned outsole.
